\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \h_{\i}\right\} _{\i\in\mathcal{I}}$
\end_inset

 be a (Hamel) basis of 
\begin_inset Formula $\Xo$
\end_inset

.
 For each 
\begin_inset Formula $\i\in\mathcal{I}$
\end_inset

 we have 
\begin_inset Formula $\h_{\i}-\Eo\h_{\i}\in\ker\Eo$
\end_inset

