\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Uo:\Xo\to\Fo:\h\mapsto\U'\left(\h-\Eo\h\right).
\]

\end_inset

Conversely, if 
\begin_inset Formula $\Uo$
\end_inset

 is a bounded Stein transform for 
\begin_inset Formula $\To$
\end_inset

